Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:44.71,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#1  废部！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:09.70,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}#2        乐器！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  差不多该起床了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八、八点了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么急事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:00:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上学去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这不是小唯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.55,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看错时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始  我就是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎新同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定加入网球部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定加入柔道部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定加入茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定加入珠算部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请一定加入…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在念叨什么啊  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在想要加入哪一个社团才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  还没决定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开学已经两周了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是运动白痴  文艺类的社团也不大了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  家里蹲就是这样子养成的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不参加社团就会变成家里蹲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头想想唯至今还没参加过什么社团活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总觉得应该做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到底要做些什么才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去参观社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观社团？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去参观轻音部啦 轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我打算加入文艺部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入部申请书也写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撕！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊  律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  废部了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确的说是即将废部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年为止的部员全部毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是本月内没有四个人加入就会被废部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以音乐室里才一个人都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  接下来有音乐课
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦  轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把这些资料发给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯着看了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.35,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢半拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.86,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨手笨脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废部的话那就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去文艺部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有部员的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说现在加入的话我就成部长了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  刚才说的轻音部是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「轻音」是指「轻松的音乐」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松的…  音乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  轻松的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Fight！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐等入部申请者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想参观一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观轻音部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是合唱部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要加入轻音部？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  合唱部…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正缺部员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  一定不会让你后悔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有你这么强行拉人加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的约定是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敲鼓  澪弹贝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…不是一直说要一起组乐队的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是约好了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去演唱会的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.21,0:08:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候说的都是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的回想明明是你虚构的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个啊  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组乐队吧  乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候律硬要组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪也说过要组乐队的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说好了转职业之后演出费我七你三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要捏造事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我只能弹一点电子琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌弃的话请让我也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:09:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子就只差一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经把我也算进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫琴吹紬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鼓手田井中律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是贝斯手秋山澪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一个…  吉他手是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得进了高中  我也想做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不知道该做些什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再点一份薯条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次来快餐店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想被问一次「不再点一份薯条吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  作战会议开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是在本月内再增加一位部员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们接下来要想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说现在入部的话可以得到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好处？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  比如说奖励一些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子或是别墅什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有诱惑力但是恐怕做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃冰淇淋或者是帮忙做作业什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人会为了这个入部的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好没意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议的人自己烦了像什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来想个法子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  总之先…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.42,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部  一起来组乐队吧  吉他手募集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月份也只剩下一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有人加入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐队都没能组成就废部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.07,0:11:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不能容忍!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻…音乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯拍得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定先加入轻音部试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活动内容是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然写轻松的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定都是些简单的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像吹吹口哨什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么社团啊一点干劲都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  好像是要组乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我不会弹吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你会什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响板…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入部申请者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮的茶具  不过喝完后要收拾好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子不用废部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽唯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当响亮的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弹吉他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  强势部员加入！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不走过这里的话就去不到轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部在音乐室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然方才加入难以说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是告诉他们我要退出好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过轻音部里都是些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  竟然说想退出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为轻音部是想来就来  想走就走的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我不是要来加入的  不是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢半拍  笨手笨脚  天然呆的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就是平泽唯同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申请入部的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那样子误会你真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吉他技术很高超吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很深的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  入部申请者来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无上欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬  快准备上茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃退部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学想要演奏什么类型的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的吉他手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不会弹吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…  其…  其…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jimi Hendrix？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  其…  其…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy Page？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeff Beck？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字「J」打头的吉他手那么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Jeff Beck啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说「摇滚吉他手只有两种」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeff Beck和Jeff Beck以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeff Beck是一位不断追求新颖音色  具有挑战精神的吉他手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是平泽同学  真有眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有像平泽同学这么出色的人加入真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周内要是再凑不齐四个人就会被废部了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越难开口了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我必须说！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  其实我过来是想请求退部的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会弹吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我以为是演奏别的什么乐器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你会什么乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响…  口琴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口琴的话我这里有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.21,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我不会吹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然想加入我们部就是说对音乐有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有其他想加入的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能就此放过这来之不易的冤大头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不被废部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须把她留住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉  我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再喝一杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有饼干和松糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱饵战术…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我本不是想过来吃东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们就这样子一起吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.07,0:17:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点跑题…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平泽同学还喜欢其他什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是问你吃的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放假的时候在家里都做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所事事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢可爱的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢的东西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷热天都不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天整天躲被炉里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天在地板上滚来滚去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难对付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么出招…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走  求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是挂名在我们部也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会带更多好吃的点心过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我随随便便填写了申请书…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让你们这么期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么道歉才好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们不对 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉强留着你是我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那至少请听一次我们的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我演奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二  三  四!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说  用语言难以表达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当头一棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过给人一种很开心的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加入贵部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  作为轻音部开始活动的纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:34.91,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我的相机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我对乐器一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以当经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我们不是体育社团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以此为契机开始学习吉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吉他好像很难的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会把懂得的教给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了刚才的演奏我觉得我也可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是加入了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对方无论如何希望我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是当经纪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这么说真不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是作为正式部员加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是会从头开始教我吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说要买新吉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道部里会不会借给我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五千日元左右能买到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓了个这样的孩子没问题吗  轻音部…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.05,0:23:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这三位是轻音部的同伴
